      "title": "[New Atlas] VW gives California camper van game-changing 4-season comfort boost",
      "content_html": "<img src=\"https://assets.newatlas.com/dims4/default/da76938/2147483647/strip/true/crop/2344x1231+0+167/resize/1200x630!/quality/85/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fnewatlas-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F79%2F59%2F36c68eeb4b21a38e1922dc819b74%2Fgeneration-side-16zu9-002.jpg&amp;na.image_optimisation=0\" style=\"width:100%;max-height:300px;object-fit:cover;\" />\n<img src=\"https://assets.newatlas.com/dims4/default/da76938/2147483647/strip/true/crop/2344x1231+0+167/resize/1200x630!/quality/85/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fnewatlas-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F79%2F59%2F36c68eeb4b21a38e1922dc819b74%2Fgeneration-side-16zu9-002.jpg&amp;na.image_optimisation=0\" style=\"width:100%;max-height:300px;object-fit:cover;\" />\n<img src=\"https://assets.newatlas.com/dims4/default/da76938/2147483647/strip/true/crop/2344x1231+0+167/resize/1200x630!/quality/85/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fnewatlas-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F79%2F59%2F36c68eeb4b21a38e1922dc819b74%2Fgeneration-side-16zu9-002.jpg&amp;na.image_optimisation=0\" style=\"width:100%;max-height:300px;object-fit:cover;\" />\n<img src=\"https://assets.newatlas.com/dims4/default/da76938/2147483647/strip/true/crop/2344x1231+0+167/resize/1200x630!/quality/85/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fnewatlas-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F79%2F59%2F36c68eeb4b21a38e1922dc819b74%2Fgeneration-side-16zu9-002.jpg&amp;na.image_optimisation=0\" style=\"width:100%;max-height:300px;object-fit:cover;\" />\n<p><img alt=\"The all-new Multivan and California Generation special editions are just the tip of the iceberg in a mid-cycle refresh Volkswagen announced this month\" src=\"https://assets.newatlas.com/dims4/default/df1e3ec/2147483647/strip/true/crop/2344x1564+0+0/resize/1439x960!/format/webp/quality/85/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fnewatlas-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F79%2F59%2F36c68eeb4b21a38e1922dc819b74%2Fgeneration-side-16zu9-002.jpg\" /><p>Just two years ago, Volkswagen launched a new California, but the iconic camper van is already up for a refresh. Along with the Multivan underneath it, the California gets a new look, sharpened interface and improved driver-assistance package. Best of all, a new climate control feature promises to make camping more comfortable throughout the entire year. Combine all that that with existing features like an available PHEV powertrain and indoor/outdoor kitchen design, and we'd say Volkswagen has quietly introduced the best California ever.</p><p><a href=\"https://newatlas.com/campervans/volkswagen-refreshed-multivan-camper/\">Continue Reading</a></p><p><b>Category:</b> <a href=\"https://newatlas.com/campervans/\">Campervans</a>, <a href=\"https://newatlas.com/adventure-vehicles/\">Adventure Vehicles</a>, <a href=\"https://newatlas.com/outdoors/\">Outdoors</a></p><p><b>Tags:</b> <a href=\"https://newatlas.com/tag/volkswagen/\" rel=\"tag\">Volkswagen</a>, <a href=\"https://newatlas.com/tag/campervan/\" rel=\"tag\">Campervan</a>, <a href=\"https://newatlas.com/tag/rv/\" rel=\"tag\">RV</a>, <a href=\"https://newatlas.com/tag/minivan/\" rel=\"tag\">Minivan</a>, <a href=\"https://newatlas.com/tag/camping/\" rel=\"tag\">Camping</a>, <a href=\"https://newatlas.com/tag/plug-in-hybrid/\" rel=\"tag\">Plug-in Hybrid</a>, <a href=\"https://newatlas.com/tag/phev/\" rel=\"tag\">PHEV</a>, <a href=\"https://newatlas.com/tag/outdoor/\" rel=\"tag\">Outdoors and Camping</a></p>",
